Medes - A Web Application runtime

Sean Hodges, 2007


Compiling the source
--------------------

Medes depends on the following components, corresponding Ubuntu packages are in brackets:
- CMake			(cmake)
- GCC & make	(build-essential)
- pkg-config	(pkg-config)
- gtkmozembed 	(firefox-dev or libxul-dev)
- GTK 2.x		(libgtk2.0-dev)
- XML2			(libxml2-dev)
- libboost		(libboost-filesystem-dev)

Perform the following steps to compile and install:

mkdir build && cd build
ccmake ../
make
sudo make install


